{"tid":2381664,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有無揸開Uber嘅師兄教路?如果全職揸有咩要留意??","createTime":"2021-01-26T18:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T06:26:52.000Z","uid":126626,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"82f148afacfdfdcae4dd194dd98bcc514a6c9a08","tid":2381664,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T18:32:30.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n<br />\n我做開Audit，本來想轉行教書，呢個願望暫時無變，都做緊相關工作。<br />\n<br />\n不過又要去讀書又要再搵工，幾年之前買咗樓，屋企人而家失左業，變咗顧唔到兩邊。<br />\n<br />\n架車早排放咗，因為要車屋企人，所以我要買架新車。如果想買一搵食車，有冇乜嘢攻略？唔係好識&hellip;&hellip;所以想問吓大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be5a39c89359242d3935001f24c3681363d11b3","tid":2381664,"uid":25727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T18:33:38.000Z","msg":"買架的士"},{"pid":"06ad65d18e7479145992e80bf7966fe11a4ae7f1","tid":2381664,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T18:46:12.000Z","msg":"全職你渣的士或者VAN 好過啦"},{"pid":"1d46224465d51f87ff88d5dd5647461a00ea4c57","tid":2381664,"uid":126626,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"06ad65d18e7479145992e80bf7966fe11a4ae7f1","tid":2381664,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T18:46:12.000Z","msg":"全職你渣的士或者VAN 好過啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T18:52:44.000Z","msg":"比Uber好？<br />\n<br />\n其實渣的士我都有考慮過，學歷嗰啲我已經放低咗，不過因為本身都要買車，我姨媽糖尿病好嚴重，行路唔方便，呢排要照顧佢。<br />\n<br />\n如果渣的士，但係自己又有架車會唔會好戇居？定係其實好多人都係咁？"},{"pid":"772f2aac5ea15591ee1359c1dd2b991c17d79b76","tid":2381664,"uid":117584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"uberd單比撚曬dc9 uber做唔過又怕比人捉 做dc9好過"},{"pid":"dd2cd46d4ec6408d64b108ef63c531bb8bd1d650","tid":2381664,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d46224465d51f87ff88d5dd5647461a00ea4c57","tid":2381664,"uid":126626,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"06ad65d18e7479145992e80bf7966fe11a4ae7f1","tid":2381664,"uid":294,"like":0,"disli